These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, black, chestnut, blood-red
House: townhouse, futuristic, farmhouse, cape-cod
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
2. the person who likes azure is the cape-cod house##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
4. the person who likes black is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | blood-red | chestnut | black | azure   |
| House   | futuristic  | townhouse     | farmhouse   | cape-cod |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, game, bluemaster, blend
There 4 different types of food: potato, grapefruit, nectarine, raspberry
1. the blend-smoker is the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the game-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | blend | game | tiparillo    |
| Food   | nectarine    | grapefruit      | potato | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, bus, quad-bike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, baseball, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Transport         | boat | quad-bike | bus   | jet-ski |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | baseball | snowboarding | lacrosse         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, rat, lizard, frog
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, fanta, coffee
1. the person drinking milk is the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Pet   | frog | rat | mouse  | lizard      |
| Beverage         | milk | coffee   | fanta | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, trike, bike, taxi
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, water, cola
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Transport   | taxi | bike | trike | train |
| Beverage    | iced-tea       | cola | water | 7up     |

