.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, magic-tricks, card-games, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, cola, soy-milk
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | board-games | magic-tricks |
| Beverage           | juice      | cola | soy-milk | almond-milk    |

