.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting, surfing
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, argentine, australian, japanese
1. the australian is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
4. the argentine is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Sport   | weightlifting | rowing | basketball | surfing  |
| Nationality           | australian | chinese | japanese       | argentine |

