.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, climbing, ice-hockey, baseball
House: futuristic, cottage, victorian, ranch-style
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the ranch-style house is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the cottage house##1
5. the futuristic house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | basketball      | climbing | baseball |
| House   | futuristic          | cottage | victorian     | ranch-style    |

