.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, milk, iced-tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, sunflower, daisy, zinnia
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite    | milk       | lemonade | iced-tea   |
| Flower     | sunflower | daisy | zinnia   | marigold |

