.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
City: miami, london, rome, venice
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, brown, purple, blue
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
4. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| City    | miami | rome  | london | venice |
| Color   | blue | purple | brown          | mauve    |

