.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, teacher, fisherman, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, thriller, horror, epic
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the scientist is on the right of the dancer##1
4. the fisherman is on the far left##1
5. the teacher is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Job      | fisherman | teacher  | dancer | scientist |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | horror | epic           | thriller   |

