2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Beverage   | milk | coffee | tea | fanta  |
| Transport           | quad-bike | scooter      | skateboard | snowmobile |

