3. the person who's sport is basketball is the turkish##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Sport   | basketball | handball  | skiing | snowboarding   |
| Nationality        | turkish | pakistani | brazilian    | french |

