.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, purple, coral, lavender
There 4 different types of food: kale, asparagus, garlic, artichoke
1. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Color           | aquamarine | lavender    | purple    | coral |
| Food   | asparagus      | garlic | kale | artichoke       |

