.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, zucchini, potato, orange
4 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, horse, bird
1. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person eating orange##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating potato##1
4. the person eating orange is the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food   | pepper | potato | zucchini | orange   |
| Pet     | horse  | dog    | chinchilla       | bird |

 